      "updated_at": "2016-03-09 14:01:46 UTC",
      "body": "Good question. I don't have any strong feelings about this. I just feel like if you open a brace, you should always go the next line, and the closing brace should be on its own line. It's mostly a consistency argument.\r\n\r\nBut it's really not a priority. In fact our coding style encourages *not* to write the `{}` at all in that case."
    },
